        title: 'What are the different types of sanitary pads?',
        content:
          'Disposable sanitary pads are used once and then thrown away and reusable sanitary pads are cloth pads that can be washed and reused many times. \r\n\r\nPads come in different shapes and sizes and have different capacities to absorb heavy or light menstrual flow. \r\n\r\nYou can experiment with different sanitary pads to decide what best suits different days of your period.',
        category: 'Managing menstruation',
