        title: 'How do I use a sanitary pad or cloth?',
        content:
          'Place the sticky part of the disposable pad, or bottom of your folded cloth, onto the crotch of your underwear. Do not insert the pad in your vagina. Change the pad or cloth every 2â€“6 hours or whenever you think it is full. \r\n\r\nFor reusable cloths or pads, wash first with cold water, then with hot water and mild soap, and dry in the sun or iron before reusing.',
        category: 'Managing menstruation',
        subCategory: 'Sanitary protection',
        live: true,
